{"tid":1262483,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實我好後悔發夢出咗去","createTime":"2019-06-27T17:01:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-27T20:11:22.000Z","uid":258069,"like":68,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"035651a2d068e3dbd28b1529cbd1f5e6b57a210b","tid":1262483,"uid":258069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T17:01:48.000Z","msg":"之前有個po 就講我返台灣睇醫生啦<br />\n<br />\n發夢喺香港吸完催淚彈唔舒服然喺台灣睇醫生<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1256338\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1256338</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n夢入面，我係一個喺台灣讀書嘅華僑二代嚟，<br />\n因為家父遲咗半年中出我老母，<br />\n所以得本廁所板Passport。<br />\n<br />\n兩三年前我發夢見到自己有權拎老母原生國嘅護照，<br />\n條件係識講當地話同返去發展（因為細個冇喺嗰度住）。<br />\n即係話我根本唔使理香港政治，直接目標去移民就得。<br />\n即使唔去老母原生國，我都可以留喺台灣。<br />\n<br />\n而我夢入邊嗰啲有出去嘅朋友，<br />\n一係就有外國passport，一係就Mix，一係就大撚把錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我哋根本唔使出去搏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我覺得我哋都真係好on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n尤其我特登洗成個生活費喺外埠返嚟搏命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搞到而家連K 都唱唔到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （氣管唔得呀）<br />\n有好日子邊個會噉樣搏命吖大佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nDLLM 因為呢度先係我哋屋企呀！<br />\n就算我哋移咗民，但對我哋嚟講香港先係我哋屋企呀！<br />\n我哋係華僑二代，我哋係Mix，So what? <br />\n國家興亡，匹夫有責！<br />\n連我哋呢啲走得嘅都咁撚搏，<br />\n冇得走嘅係咪應該更加要保護呢個家？<br />\n<br />\n後悔？我一啲都唔後悔，冇錢可以再揾，去邊度都一樣，<br />\n但屋企冇咗就係冇咗，<br />\n加油呀！香港人！"},{"pid":"373960fc45d7f3bf274bf66faca7cfb678a94eca","tid":1262483,"uid":7919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T17:06:05.000Z","msg":"支持!<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"987ba386305c27ec826cb2e890f971d3929ec065","tid":1262483,"uid":23189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T17:13:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a070c3766b2c3d439f0b33921037656784cf1e2f","tid":1262483,"uid":245523,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T17:15:31.000Z","msg":"好奇一問 你咩血統<br />\n我都識人揸外國passport 都有岀 雖然可能只係嚟睇熱鬧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc9f01a91328d6e538a94cff57eca24c3ecf2f80","tid":1262483,"uid":258069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a070c3766b2c3d439f0b33921037656784cf1e2f","tid":1262483,"uid":245523,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T17:15:31.000Z","msg":"好奇一問 你咩血統<br />\n我都識人揸外國passport 都有岀 雖然可能只係嚟睇熱鬧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T17:24:02.000Z","msg":"我哋成班都係南島mix 嚟 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n膚色比較深色啲同輪廓少少唔同 但都係華人樣<br />\n我自己就好白 華人樣 但啡頭髮<br />\n我哋呢班南島mix 由前線到運書咩都有"},{"pid":"808bad94a0b06a7d2feb9740f7c390166448f8f2","tid":1262483,"uid":210794,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T17:29:39.000Z","msg":"MK啲講<br />\n今次博盡無悔！"},{"pid":"8ae7a32e9aa1f2cc5946cc408c514206782a25c8","tid":1262483,"uid":258069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T17:45:16.000Z","msg":"講多樣嘢畀大家知，<br />\n媽媽冇乜讀書，唔明發生乜事，<br />\n但佢由我發夢反國教嗰日已經同我講，<br />\n我唔明你哋做緊咩，但只要你認為啱嘅，你就去做啦。<br />\n<br />\n長輩唔出嚟佢可能真係單純唔明，<br />\n是緊要係等佢知你做緊啲啱嘅嘢。<br />\n<br />\n已經準備喺個夢度幫佢轉走啲錢同送佢返鄉下種香蕉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5264cd86ce89934907eb56d5aea499d1db10f57c","tid":1262483,"uid":9214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T19:26:26.000Z","msg":"我發夢鼻水有血絲<br />\n上顎冇左知覺<br />\n不過過兩日冇事"},{"pid":"afdcd93d62845460d87e9f45060003b04c59305e","tid":1262483,"uid":74888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T20:11:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}